{"tid":43704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"帽事既......","createTime":"2016-12-17T16:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T14:01:19.000Z","uid":42561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d280db85781d3f4590cbfe51201ab569db40b1dc","tid":43704,"uid":42561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"有冇試過戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既巴絲可以分享下往事？<br />\n<br />\n例如一齊左幾耐, 戴之前有咩先兆, 戴左幾耐先知同埋對方係咩人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同另一半一齊左好耐, 視佢為結婚對象<br />\n不過佢最近變左好多, 覺得帽不久矣<br />\n希望係自己諗多左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161c2d32f0677e7b19e9fc5de1478f0659f65020","tid":43704,"uid":42561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c4ec8dadcd30ee46331afc039ee0c6fc2fa0fb","tid":43704,"uid":16253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"先兆=變咗好多"},{"pid":"0b44a7df62b874e25c23958b9bd5cc9b1ea1e798","tid":43704,"uid":42561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先兆=變咗好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想聽下詳細版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be84bc2dc3168f68d43e53a03b8025fbb3e2799","tid":43704,"uid":14413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:38:09.000Z","ms